{"tid":1235952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港金融沙皇) 任志剛：林鄭盡心為香港服務　支持其續任特首","createTime":"2019-06-17T09:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:00:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ea897f4327cf7b9b688b9c5dfb0d9b9949fc06","tid":1235952,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/08/10210853_136951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F08%2F10210853_136951.jpg&h=3fe236f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府修訂《逃犯條例》觸發大批市民遊行抗議，行政長官林鄭月娥最終宣布暫緩修例。行政會議成員任志剛表示，林鄭月娥一直盡心為香港服務，支持她繼續擔任行政長官。<br />\n<br />\n任志剛表示，政府前日已表示暫緩執行修訂《逃犯條例》，實事求是地說暫緩執行，其實已是撤回。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，相信大部分學生都是和平理性表達訴求，當中只有小部分是害群之馬，使用暴力，破壞社會秩序。他希望事件可以告一段落，讓社會重回正軌，畢竟香港仍面對很大挑戰，政府還有大量工作需要處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/06/17/010119282.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F010119282.shtml&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=2ad9ccd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/06/17/010119282.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"3ad6e3d07069d9990dfd448c9cdc412e7f51f911","tid":1235952,"uid":109136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"收皮啦白龜頭"},{"pid":"8b8b5d87febd9f8d4b27fc7f8ece0bd0cf8022b1","tid":1235952,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:58:44.000Z","msg":"無貢獻嘅垃圾"},{"pid":"0478ccc4a792c70c2b7b1a6ff0980ae594b85fa6","tid":1235952,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"似玩鳩林鄭"},{"pid":"cc6847008c76903c4ca04204756adbdc56d187b6","tid":1235952,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"又加返d柴，任狗真古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hk